	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;建立SHM系统流程&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;160&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;385px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;shm系统价值&#34;&gt;SHM系统价值
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;参考文献：&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;PSA: Svendsen et al., 2021, The use of digital solutions and structural health monitoring for integrity management of offshore structures, Rambøll report no. REN2021N00099-RAM-RP-00004 dated 14th February 2022&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;引入SHM系统的主要目的是减少不确定性；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;同时SHM系统还能够提供用于优化检查计划的其他信息&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB1structural-health-monitoring-by-use-of-sensor-data/image-20250225192219780.png&#34;
	width=&#34;909&#34;
	height=&#34;322&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB1structural-health-monitoring-by-use-of-sensor-data/image-20250225192219780_hu_d16ea7c37143c966.png 480w, https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB1structural-health-monitoring-by-use-of-sensor-data/image-20250225192219780_hu_b63856477ef4d9ad.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;在海上结构中使用SHM创造的价值及收益&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;282&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;677px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;表1：使用SHM系统为海上结构创造的价值&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
