	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;RBI作为选择TBI/CBI的基础&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;248&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;595px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calendar-based inspection vs conditional-based inspection&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB1structural-health-monitoring-by-use-of-sensor-data/image-20250225193442952.png&#34;
